  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    com.getmoneytree.MoneytreeLink.client() 
    com.getmoneytree.MoneytreeLink.connectService(Activity, String)
    Use MoneytreeLink.openVault(int, LinkRequestContext) instead, providing in LinkRequestContext.Builder.path(String) any of the VAULT_* path values (here "service") and your serviceId in LinkRequestContext.Builder.pathSuffix(String).
    com.getmoneytree.MoneytreeLink.connectService(Activity, String, Action.OnCompletionListener)
    Use MoneytreeLink.openVault(int, LinkRequestContext) instead, providing in LinkRequestContext.Builder.path(String) any of the VAULT_* path values (here "service") and your serviceId in LinkRequestContext.Builder.pathSuffix(String).
    com.getmoneytree.MoneytreeLinkConfiguration.isProduction()
    use linkEnvironment instead
    com.getmoneytree.MoneytreeLinkConfiguration.Builder.isProduction(boolean)
    use linkEnvironment instead
    com.getmoneytree.MoneytreeLink.openCustomerSupport(Activity)
    Use MoneytreeLink.openVault(int, LinkRequestContext) instead providing in LinkRequestContext.Builder.path(String) any of the VAULT_* path values (here "customer-support")
    com.getmoneytree.MoneytreeLink.openCustomerSupport(Activity, Action.OnCompletionListener)
    Use MoneytreeLink.openVault(int, LinkRequestContext) instead providing in LinkRequestContext.Builder.path(String) any of the VAULT_* path values (here "customer-support")
    com.getmoneytree.MoneytreeLink.openServices(Activity, VaultOpenServicesOptions)
    Use MoneytreeLink.openVault(int, LinkRequestContext) instead, providing in LinkRequestContext.Builder.vaultOpenServicesOptions(VaultOpenServicesOptions) the VaultOpenServicesOptions you need.
    com.getmoneytree.MoneytreeLink.openServices(Activity, VaultOpenServicesOptions, Action.OnCompletionListener)
    Use MoneytreeLink.openVault(int, LinkRequestContext) instead, providing in LinkRequestContext.Builder.vaultOpenServicesOptions(VaultOpenServicesOptions) the VaultOpenServicesOptions you need.
    com.getmoneytree.MoneytreeLink.openVaultFrom(Activity)
    will be removed after 5.3.x. Use the MoneytreeLink.openVault(int, com.getmoneytree.LinkRequestContext)
    com.getmoneytree.MoneytreeLink.openVaultFrom(Activity, Action.OnCompletionListener)
    will be removed after 5.3.x. Use MoneytreeLink.openVault(int, com.getmoneytree.LinkRequestContext)
    com.getmoneytree.MoneytreeLink.openVaultFrom(Activity, Action.OnCompletionListener, String)
    will be removed after 5.3.x. Use MoneytreeLink.openVault(int, com.getmoneytree.LinkRequestContext)
    com.getmoneytree.MoneytreeLink.serviceSettings(Activity, String)
    Use MoneytreeLink.openVault(int, LinkRequestContext) instead, providing in LinkRequestContext.Builder.path(String) any of the VAULT_* path values (here "connection") and your serviceId in LinkRequestContext.Builder.pathSuffix(String).
    com.getmoneytree.MoneytreeLink.serviceSettings(Activity, String, Action.OnCompletionListener)
    Use MoneytreeLink.openVault(int, LinkRequestContext) instead, providing in LinkRequestContext.Builder.path(String) any of the VAULT_* path values (here "connection") and your serviceId in LinkRequestContext.Builder.pathSuffix(String).
